    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体一物一检规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1219533846010269696",
    "content": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台个人/个体一物一检规则》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年3月31日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年4月6日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年4月7日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">修订一物一检酒类商品质量不合格、主观恶意逃避或躲避入仓查验以及商品假冒伪劣等其他违规行为的定义和处理措施</span> <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">。</span></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">原规则链接：<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1155375425137020928&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1155375425137020928&amp;btype=12</a></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">修订部分如下：</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 396.0pt; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"528\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 15.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 101.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"135\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 118.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"157\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 177.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 15.0pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"236\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 90.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 101.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 90.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"135\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">7.1.1.1 A</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">级不合格 经入仓一物一检认定为重度瑕疵等情形；</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 118.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 90.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"157\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（4）陈年老酒：严重破损、明显漏液；瓶帽异常（拔头）、瓶身打孔；整箱产品吹箱；防伪标明显异常。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 177.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 90.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"236\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（4）陈年老酒：商品与订单信息不符（商品存在实物名称、品牌、系列-老发新等与订单信息不符的情形），整箱产品吹箱；正品但防伪标明显异常等无法下发消费者的重度瑕疵质量问题。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 72.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 101.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 72.5pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"135\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">7.1.1.2 B</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">级不合格 经入仓鉴定/鉴别认定为中度瑕疵等情形</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 118.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 72.5pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"157\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（3）陈年老酒：防伪标缺失；酒标、瓶帽磨损；瓶口松动；瓶口齿痕磨损、断裂；瓶身掉漆；盖帽突起。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 177.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 72.5pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"236\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（3）陈年老酒：产品破损、漏液、防伪标缺失；酒标、瓶帽磨损；瓶口松动；瓶口齿痕磨损、断裂；瓶身掉漆；盖帽突起。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 130.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 101.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.5pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"135\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">7.1.1.3 C</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">级不合格 经入仓鉴定/鉴别认定为轻度瑕疵等情形；</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 118.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.5pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"157\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">轻度瑕疵其他标准：（1）陈年老酒：酒液高度差异；商品与实物不符（发错货等）；缺配件（例：酒杯等）；防伪标轻度划痕、气泡等；酒液酒渍以及其他轻微脏污，不影响饮用；外包装轻微破损划痕。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 177.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.5pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"236\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">轻度瑕疵其他标准：（1）陈年老酒：外包装轻微破损划痕；酒液高度差异；缺配件（例：酒杯等）；防伪标轻度划痕、气泡等；酒液酒渍以及其他轻微脏污，不影响正常饮用。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 29.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 101.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 29.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"135\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">8.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">处理措施</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 118.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 29.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"157\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">情节极其严重，每单1000元</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 177.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 29.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"236\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">情节轻微，每单1000元；情节严重/极其严重：每单5000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 43.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 101.0pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 43.5pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"135\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">9.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">处理措施</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 118.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 43.5pt;\" valign=\"bottom\" width=\"157\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">情节轻微：<br />第一次违规，店铺预警、删除违规商品销量</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 177.0pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 43.5pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"236\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">情节轻微：<br />第一次违规，店铺预警</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
